; font5x7.mac — the classic 5x7 dot-matrix font, ASCII 040..0177
;
; Pascal Stang's font5x7 (avrlib, 2001), public 5x7 dot-matrix set.
; 5 column bytes per glyph, column-major, bit 0 = top row.
; Shared by the max7219 and vqc10 drivers (label: FONT).

; ---- 5x7 font, ASCII 040..0177, 5 column bytes per glyph -----------
; Pascal Stang font5x7 (avrlib, 2001). Column-major, bit 0 = top row.

